column2: "The Darker presence here is quite dense."
"If Master Gettemhart were here, he would partake in the utmost violent jubilation."
"Somehow, it feels nostalgic. Not much time has passed, and yet it feels so very distant."
"When I first met Master Gettemhart, he was not the severe individual everyone has come to know him as."
"He was someone who helped me when I was new and naive, and he wasn't hated by Zeno."
"But the one who destroyed that was me..."
"Ten years ago... Darkers attacked... Dark Falz Apprentice appeared..."
"In order to protect me, right when I had just set out...."
